{
  "stem": "747.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one day, they took the mother and the girl wanted to kill herself, but she couldn't do much.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's just-- there's a built-in self preservation that nobody wanted to-- volunteered to take me to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got very close with the immediate who were around me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we, we knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We felt everybody's pain and each other's pain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time, definitely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw the chimney was burning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- and when a big transport came in, then it-- they had-- they closed up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody was allowed to go out from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we knew that a transport arrived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't want we should see it, and didn't want we should be panic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So while-- and after that, the chimney was burning day and night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we knew that another transport of unfortunate people were killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, that was a place where everything was a mountain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mountain of eye glasses, a mountain of, of everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to open up the suitcases and the bags, whatever people brought with them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And most of them, their best thing they tried to bring, not knowing, not even-- that they are not going to be able to use it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had to sort it out and made it into big bales and everything went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything that was good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Shoes, and clothes, and beddings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Food was very little.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Approximately 500.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not there.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was strictly women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The men came after to pick up the bales, what we packed together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they carried it to the station to ship it out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was painful because we were close to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
